This directory contains the files from libnodave.

This distribution of libnodave is based on libnodave 0.8.4.6 and has been 
modified for use with the EPICS s7nodave driver. It only consists of those
files needed by the s7nodave driver. For the original distribution please go to
http://libnodave.sourceforge.net/.

